title: Spring STAMPEDE
body_text:
Attendance
: 20, comprised of 14 men and 6 women.
New Dodgeballers
: (1) John Keynton
Game Rules
: Classic two-team.
Featured Match
: Team ONE defeated Team TWO, 4 - 2
Game-By-Game Results
: ONE 2-5; TWO 1, 6
→ The scheduled match between "Rookie" Arthur Casbarro and "Legend" Kevin Fitzpatrick did not occur due to Casbarro's mysterious no-show. Thus, teams were arranged via "The Writer".
Musical Playlist
: Kevin Fitzpatrick
Online Exclusive!
Team ONE ~ John Tronolone, Alysha Kelly, Travis Mills, Kevin Fitzpatrick, Justin Wolf, Kenny Jacobs, Chris Adams, Joanice Lima, Melissa Kerr, Juan Londono.
Team TWO ~ Lauren Stopa, Justin Pierce, Kelly Oberto, John Keynton, Kevin Adams, Dan Turner, Mike "Sputz" Krott, Jason Teitelbaum, Ray Marzarella, Diana DiBuccio.
________________________________________
_______________________________________
Attendance
: 11, comprised of 9 men and 2 women.
New Dodgeballers
: (1) Rob Blake
→ This was the third lowest attendance for any
Tronolone Era
event. Only
DODGEBALL 45
and
DODGEBALL 62
had fewer participants with 10 and 5, respectively.
→ This was the first time since
DODGEBALL LX SEVEN
there were less than 10 male players as well.
Game Rules
: Classic two-team.
Featured Match
: Team TWO defeated Team ONE, 7 - 3
Game-By-Game Results
: ONE 3, 5, 6; TWO 1, 2, 4, 7-10
→ Due to the unpredictable weather and surprising low turnout, the Joanice Lima vs. Lauren Stopa contest was postponed. Like the previous event, teams were formed by "The Writer".
Musical Playlist
: Kevin Fitzpatrick
Online Exclusive!
Team ONE ~ John Tronolone, Joanice Lima, Justin Pierce, Justin Wolf, Bobby Vetrano, Rob Blake.
Team TWO ~ Kenny Jacobs, Chris Adams, Lauren Stopa, Kevin Fitzpatrick, Kevin Megill.
